devdoc.author: Iain Nash @isiain
devdoc.details: Contract for Algo Lite Project by @jawn +

constructor.details: Sets up the serial contract with a name, symbol, and an initial allowed creator.Mints the genesis token to the deployer.

params._maxAvailableId: Max number that can be minted beyond 0
params.name: Name of NFT contract

mint(address).details: Authenticated mint function that mints a random available NFT

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setIsApprovedMinter(address,bool).details: Admin owner-only function to update the list of approved minters

params.minter: list of addresses that are approved minters

params.interfaceId: interface id to match to erc165 standard

tokenURI(uint256).details: Returns tokenURI for given token that exists

params.tokenId: id of token to retrieve metadata for

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
